FIND YOUR
WEEKENDESK CAREER!

Weekendesk is the European leader for packaged short-break travel!

Our business is to bring fun, pleasure and relaxation to our clients: our
young and energetic team of more than 150 employees,

from 15 nationalities is working hard to make it happen in our Paris and
Barcelona offices.



     * Single Edit
     * Column Edit

   IFRAME: https://www.youtube.com/embed/SPCe1Mn3LPM?feature=oembed

     * Single Edit
     * Column Edit

Our success story starts with a single word: Weekend!

   Weekendesk has stayed attached to its core mission since the beginning
   in 2008: offering exciting experiences to people looking to go away on
   a short break.

   At Weekendesk, we believe life is what you do with your time here:
   browse our website and let us help you find the perfect activity to
   share with your friends and family.

   With Weekendesk, you build memories you will remember fondly.



